data.description: Beautiful single family home in Colony Woods which is a quiet 55+ community located in Central Boca Raton. This home boasts three bedrooms with a oversized master suite. The third bedroom is currently being used as a den with built in desk. The kitchen and bathrooms have been updated and the laundry room is inside the home. Per the association, the cars must be parked in the garage overnight. Make your appointment to view it today, All information provided is deemed reliable but not guaranteed. Everything should be independently verified by the buyer. Broker/Agent is not responsible for any typos or inaccuracies.
